{"tid":1463683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我之前是在機場接機的，而我接機的原則是： 「幹你娘塞爆」","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:35.000Z","uid":177525,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b91549aca9ce6f32bf36755f2a56f85d062ed6b6","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"我之前是在機場接機的，而我接機的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管機場運作三小的，每次接機就是姬芭一堆人的。小人企滿接機大堂，多人企上離境大堂。超多人企完T1送T2，跟把整個機場的位置企滿沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月接機25天，林鄭跑來跟我說，這個月機場休息二十六天，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"b74ac557d601f8433340f636d53ec7d688b18062","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"34bf5fa412c86ec4493bcaee293043e3fc598da5","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"c16b9f3af1a46ca660d11b6aad48f13e6423f498","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"c6a3091e8fcc9665cb7cb879283ed5ce4e0f9445","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:39:08.000Z","msg":"814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"bb2249b04173a0681990d60851ad9a9ebdfda82e","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:39:53.000Z","msg":"814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"634c6af72d00af38b937efb63736e4d0a6f699eb","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"035b4cc23f23223a9cb71b3211538dbb60ab83e9","tid":1463683,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b77e52e041db426303ebde593ab8d8342e4b485","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"d15523149e3b05d5d62eed22540d739fd09ae4aa","tid":1463683,"uid":173541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4677658d7a312609a9696aa0c153be361d68d0d9","tid":1463683,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"ff701cb3ec8e5d870b7d3aee24dd410b5ba9f0f1","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"塞機場前分返清楚方法同結果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463381</a><br />\n<br />\n814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"545a36469de14e1bba9faf85c25ecb9f6272278b","tid":1463683,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:03:08.000Z","msg":"塞機場前分返清楚方法同結果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463381</a><br />\n<br />\n814 繼續塞"},{"pid":"356cedbb681425090cc551736f9f3ea8be074adc","tid":1463683,"uid":50075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}